title.narrative: Agricultural Development: Productive Partnerships in Agriculture Project (Papua New Guinea)

description.narrative: The main objective of the project is to improve the livelihoods of smallholder cocoa and coffee producers through improvement of the performance and sustainability of value chains in cocoa- and coffee-producing areas. A key outcome for the project is strengthening the institutional capacity and coordination of the key industry bodies contributing to improved sector policies.
